{
  "id": "adv_main_01_11_05",
  "title": "星見編3章5話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（練習が終わって、寮に戻ると）\n（居間には不思議なものが置いてあった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(After finishing practice and returning to the dorm‚)\n(we find a mysterious item in the living room.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.953408148709466,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　これは……バースデーケーキ？\n誰かの誕生日だったか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm? Is this a birthday cake?\nIs it somebody’s birthday today?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.441655508677165,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "さて、誰のでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Gee‚ who could it be?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.5749888420105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　ええと……さくらでも、琴乃でもないし……\nいや、今日誕生日のメンバーなんていないはずだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Well‚ it’s not Sakura or Kotono…\nYeah‚ nobody in either group has a birthday today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.50648540655773,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、忘れてるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ so you forgot?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.773152073224395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "マネージャー失格ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re a failure as a manager.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.373151977856963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ？　待て待て、ええと……\n……あ、もしかして俺？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Wait a minute‚ um…\nOh… Is it mine?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.1942176580429,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだったんですか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-is it really your birthday?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.81476966601152,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いや、俺の誕生日は……\n今日じゃない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No. My birthday…\n…isn’t today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.7017764733388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "ボケ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Was that a joke?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.535109806672125,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "寒いですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If so‚ it was a terrible one.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.90177647333879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "突っ込まないで。ええと……\nあと、考えられるのは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ I get it. Umm…\nThe only other person I can think of is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（俺の横をスーッと通って）\n（麻奈がケーキを覗き込む）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Mana floats past me)\n(and looks at the cake.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.92574474077958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 63.725744740779575
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 63.725744740779575
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_flashback-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 64.02574474077957
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば麻奈、誕生日だったんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ wasn’t it your birthday‚ Mana?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.85907807411292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 67.88118686737161
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "女子に言ったらマイナス一億点のセリフを\n堂々と言ったね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You just boldly said a line that’ll make you lose\n100 million points with a girl.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.88118686737158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 73.61452020070492
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（もしかして。そう気付いた時、現れた琴乃が）\n（麻奈のバースデープレートをケーキに置いた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(By the time I realize it‚ Kotono enters the room)\n(and puts Mana’s name on the birthday cake.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.94785353403823,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "はい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.7145202007049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_hope-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 81.7145202007049
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃんが、二日遅れだけど\n麻奈さんの誕生日祝いたいって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura said even though it’s two days late‚\nshe wants to celebrate Mana’s birthday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.54785353403824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "だって。良かったね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hear that? Isn’t that great?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.1245530678084,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "うん……ありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Thanks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.59707008135821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣、一体誰と話しているんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei‚ who in the world are you speaking to?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.7953921390822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　誰って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? What do you mean‚ who?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.96344195139908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣。シーー……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei. Shh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.22874806654951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "……うん\n秘密ー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah.\nNot telling.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.09541473321632,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "？\nなんなんですの、一体……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?\nWhat in the world is going on?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.96592006843376,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、早くしないと\nロウソク溶けてきちゃうわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ we need to hurry\nbefore the candles melt.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.09925340176696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、本当だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ right!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.49925340176696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "ロウソク、誰が消すんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who’s going to blow out the candles?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.39925340176696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_11_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "私、さくらに消してほしい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want Sakura to blow them out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.07759812832946,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
